data.description: The charm of an established neighborhood with a fresh new look inside! 4 bedroom, 2 bathrooms, and an office. Great quiet location close to the Greenbelt! All new flooring, paint, updated countertops, painted cabinets, new faucets, and shiplap! 2,000 sq. Ft. - 1,000 on each level. Main floor has spacious living room that features an impressive shiplap wall, three bedrooms & two baths with beautiful Carrara marble floors, open and light dining room and kitchen with dazzling subway tile backsplash, and a main floor laundry room. Basement has two finished rooms, one substantial room for a wonderful family room or a large bedroom and another room for an office with a closet. The other half of the basement is unfinished for plenty of storage or finish it the way you would like! Oversized deep one car garage with automatic door opener and shelves with work bench area. Freshly poured concrete driveway and sidewalk. Newer solid wood front door, air conditioner, dishwasher, disposal, fridge, range, ceiling fan. Fenced in back yard with a firepit.
